## Step 10 — Per-package README (English)

### 10.1 `@shady/sdk-core` README
**Path:** `packages/sdk-core/README.md`

```md
# @shady/sdk-core

Foundation utilities for the Shady SDK:
- Minimal crypto helpers (ed25519 keypair, SHA-256 KDF)
- Encoding utilities (hex ↔ bytes)
- Simple browser storage wrapper
- Typed error class

> ⚠️ Crypto functions here are **placeholders** for prototypes. Replace with audited libs and align with Shady’s on-chain programs before production.

## Install (workspace)
This package is part of the monorepo. Consumers import from the workspace:
```ts
import { Crypto, toHex } from "@shady/sdk-core";

